7}, {\"ngram\": \"gender norms\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Drawing on my own experiences as a female within the male-dominated breakdancing scene in Sydney, first as a spectator, then as an active crewmember, this thesis questions why so few female participants engage in this creative space, and how breakdancing might be a space to displace and deterritorialise gender,\\\" Dr Gunn wrote.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 2115, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1877, \"end\": 1883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999999218371189, \"rank\": 7.652819628556229e-08, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 2104, \"end\": 2108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999084703979317, \"rank\": 0.0007564311115278985, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my own experiences\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"a female\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"the male-dominated breakdancing scene\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectator\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"an active crewmember\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"this thesis\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"so few female participants\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"this creative space\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"a space\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"gender\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kyle relayed to his listeners he watched The Project on Sunday night and saw \\\"another B-boy on there\\\" who defended Raygun.\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2117, \"end\": 2121, \"title\": \"http://dbp